   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:33,685:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  The National Institute of Mental Health (NIMH) reports that ~21 million US adults experience at least
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:33,722:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: one major depressive episode annually, with approximately one-third not responding to available treatments. The
