   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,387:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 2024 | Ph3 original: 67-71% remission vs 32-48% placebo; FDA rejected on unblinding + ethics |
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,392:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: What went wrong with MDMA:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,394:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,398:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Functional unblinding:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,407:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Participants could tell if they received MDMA vs placebo (psychoactive
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,410:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: effects obvious), introducing expectation bias.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,414:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,417:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Ethical violations:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,425:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Three papers retracted from Psychopharmacology journal (Aug 2024) due to
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,429:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: unethical conduct at a study site.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,431:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,434:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Therapist misconduct allegations:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,437:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Reported during FDA review.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,441:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,444:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Cardiac safety gaps:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,447:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Limited liver function testing data.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,450:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,455:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Durability questions:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,460:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  FDA questioned long-term efficacy persistence.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,463:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,467:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Therapy confound:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,471:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Inability to separate drug effect from psychotherapy component.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,478:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,480:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Patent rejection:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,483:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  USPTO rejected MDMA particle-size patents (Jan 2025).
