   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,761:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 3.2 Academic Research Direction (Next 5–10 Years)
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,765:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Current academic trends (evidenced by published literature and conference presentations):
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,767:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  1 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,770:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Microdosing vs. macrodosing debate:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,789:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Johns Hopkins, Imperial College London, and UCSF are
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,797:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: running controlled microdosing studies. Early evidence suggests placebo-controlled effects may be
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,799:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: smaller than anecdotal reports. 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,802:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Reference: Yamamoto et al., 2024, Nature Mental Health.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,806:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,809:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Neuroplasticity mechanisms:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,819:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Research focuses on 5-HT2A receptor-mediated structural
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,822:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: neuroplasticity — psilocybin and DMT promoting dendritic spine growth. 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,827:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Reference: Ly et al., 2018,
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,830:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Cell Reports; Shao et al., 2021, Neuropsychopharmacology.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,832:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,834:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Combination therapies (drug + psychotherapy):
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,849:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  The MDMA model (drug + therapy sessions) is
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,855:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: being tested with psilocybin. The key scientific question: how much of the clinical effect is
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: pharmacological vs. psychological?
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,859:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  4 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,861:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Biomarker-guided treatment:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,881:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  EEG and fMRI studies (Beacon Biosignals, Palo Santo portfolio
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,892:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: company) are developing predictive biomarkers for psychedelic treatment response. This could
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,896:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: enable patient stratification — a commercial game-changer.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,898:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  5 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,900:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Next-generation molecules:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,917:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Deuterated analogs (Cybin CYB003/CYB004), non-hallucinogenic
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,925:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 5-HT2A agonists (Gilgamesh/AbbVie bretisilocin), and short-duration variants (Reunion
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,927:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Neuroscience RE104) aim to solve the 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,929:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,931:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: therapist time cost
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,932:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,934:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  problem.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,935:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  6 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,937:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: New indications beyond depression:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,956:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  PTSD (COMP360 Phase 2b/3 initiating), opioid use disorder
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,963:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: (ibogaine/18-MC), autism social communication (MindMed MM402), anorexia nervosa (academic
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,966:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: studies), and headache disorders (academic).
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:34,969:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 10-year prediction:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,036:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  By 2035, we expect 3–5 FDA-approved psychedelic therapeutics (psilocybin-based, MDMA if
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,083:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: trial design solves unblinding, and at least one short-acting DMT analog). The market will bifurcate into (a) clinical
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,101:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: therapeutics requiring supervised administration and (b) take-home formulations (oral, ODT) for maintenance.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,105:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Digital therapeutics (app-based therapy integration, EEG monitoring) will become standard adjuncts.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,109:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 3.3 Commercial Research Direction (Next 5–10 Years)
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,112:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  1 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,114:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Big Pharma entry via M
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,116:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: &
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,119:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: A:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,137:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  AbbVie ($1.2B Gilgamesh deal, 2025) and Otsuka ($1.23B
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,147:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Transcend deal, Jan 2026) signal that established pharma is acquiring psychedelic assets at the Phase
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,149:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 2/3 stage. Expect J
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,151:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: &
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,155:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: J (which owns Spravato/esketamine), Bristol-Myers Squibb, and Merck to
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,157:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: follow.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,159:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,161:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Platform vs. asset plays:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,175:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Compass is a single-asset company (COMP360). atai is a platform
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,179:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: (multiple portfolio companies). The market will reward platforms that can produce 2+ approved
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,182:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: assets.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,184:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,187:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Commercial model innovation:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,197:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  The key challenge is the treatment delivery model — psychedelics
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,200:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: require supervised administration (6–8 hours per session). Companies are developing:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,203:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,205:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Training networks (Compass is building a therapist training program)
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,208:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,210:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Clinic partnerships (MindMed explored with NYU Langone)
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,212:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,214:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Digital companion apps (Beacon Biosignals EEG monitoring)
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,215:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,218:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Shorter-acting molecules to reduce therapist time cost (Cybin CYB003, Reunion
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,219:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: RE104)
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,220:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  4 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,221:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Reimbursement pathway:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,242:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Critical commercial milestone. No psychedelic therapeutic is currently
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,250:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: reimbursed by insurance. Compass is engaging payors; the first reimbursement code (CPT) for
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,252:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: psychedelic-assisted therapy could emerge by 2027–2028.
