   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,586:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 4.3 Why New Solutions Work Better Than Existing Ones
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,589:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Existing standard of care for TRD:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,591:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,601:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: SSRIs/SNRIs: 30-40% response rate, 4-6 weeks onset, daily dosing, side effects (weight gain, sexual
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,604:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: dysfunction, emotional blunting). ~33% of MDD patients don
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,607:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: t respond at all.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,612:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,614:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Esketamine (Spravato, J
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,617:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: &
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: J): Intranasal, supervised administration, weekly-to-biweekly,
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,629:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ~$600-900/dose, ~28% response at 4 weeks. Requires REMS program.
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,631:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:35,634:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ECT: Effective but invasive, memory side effects, stigmatized.
