   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,337:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 7.1 Framework Selection
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,339:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: All companies are 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,341:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: pre-revenue, clinical-stage biotech
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,343:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: . Standard DCF models are not directly applicable because:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,345:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,346:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: No cash flows exist
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,348:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,349:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Approval timelines are uncertain (binary regulatory events)
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,351:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,353:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Commercial launch parameters (pricing, volume, market share) are highly speculative
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,354:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: We use a 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,356:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: three-method triangulation approach:
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,357:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  1 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,359:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Risk-Adjusted Net Present Value (rNPV)
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,361:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — industry standard for clinical-stage biotech
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,362:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,364:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Comparable Company Analysis
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,366:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — enterprise value / pipeline stage metrics
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:40:37,367:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
